description:
LIZA Token is a swap of LIZA virtual coin that is currently available on Yobit.
LIZA Token will allow investors trader to move their LIZA token over the ETH network and trade LIZA token on several exchanges as currently LIZA virtual coin is only limited to Yobit.
Yobit started denomination on LIZA coin and that result in dropping coin price.
LIZA Token will avoid the dropping coin price and allow flexibility for investors to move coins from one ETH address to another.
name: LIZA
